If you get an error in any of the nodes above make sure the files are in the correct directories.

See the top of the examples page for the links : https://comfyanonymous.github.io/ComfyUI_examples/flux/

flux1-dev.safetensors goes in: ComfyUI/models/unet/

t5xxl_fp16.safetensors and clip_l.safetensors go in: ComfyUI/models/clip/

ae.safetensors goes in: ComfyUI/models/vae/


Tip: You can set the weight_dtype above to one of the fp8 types if you have memory issues.
The reference sampling implementation auto adjusts the shift value based on the resolution, if you don't want this you can just bypass (CTRL-B) this ModelSamplingFlux node.

The redux model lets you prompt with images. It can be used with any Flux1 dev or schnell model workflow.

You can chain multiple "Apply Style Model" nodes if you want to mix multiple images together.

A beautiful and graceful Chinese woman with flowing black hair adorned with white flowers and a white ribbon. She was wearing a flowing off shoulder white dress and a delicate necklace with a pendant. The background is a peaceful sky with fluffy white clouds and sparkling lights, bringing a magical and extraordinary atmosphere to the entire scene. Authentic style.

A woman wearing a traditional Chinese qipao. Qipao is a long and elegant high necked floral embroidered dress. She held a red fan in her hand and adorned her hair with decorative elements. The background is a traditional Chinese street adorned with red lanterns and buildings, implying a festive or cultural atmosphere. The overall atmosphere is full of vitality and rich cultural atmosphere.
